      <span class="eyebrow">If you’re in danger</span>
      <h1>Crisis Support</h1>
      <p class="lead">If you’re at immediate risk, please contact local emergency services now.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="wrap">
  <section class="grid" aria-label="Immediate steps">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Right now</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Call your local emergency number (e.g., 999/112 in the UK).</li>
        <li>If possible, stay with someone you trust or go to a safe public place.</li>
        <li>Remove items you could use to harm yourself and make your environment safe.</li>
      </ol>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <h2>Speak to someone</h2>
      <p class="meta">24/7, confidential support is available in most regions.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Samaritans (UK/Ireland):</strong> 116 123 · jo@samaritans.org</li>
        <li><strong>Emergency Department:</strong> go to your nearest A&amp;E.</li>
        <li><strong>GP / Primary Care:</strong> ask for an urgent same-day appointment.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <h2>Make a tiny plan</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>One safe person you can contact</li>
        <li>One safe place you can go</li>
        <li>One tiny action (drink water, go outside, sit by a plant)</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </section>

